Name":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-xs font-mono text-coral uppercase tracking-wider","children":"Engineering"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-xs text-muted","children":"12 January 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-xs text-muted","children":"9 min read"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"font-serif text-dark leading-[1.15] mb-6","style":{"fontSize":"clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem)"},"children":"Building Payment Processing Systems: When to Use Stripe vs Custom"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-500 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-sans","children":"Stripe is great for simple payments. But for complex billing, multiple payment methods, or specific compliance needs, custom payment systems win."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-[#EEEEEE] mb-10"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10","children":[["$","span","payments",{"className":"text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"payments"}],["$","span","billing",{"className":"text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"billing"}],["$","span","fintech",{"className":"text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"fintech"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-goated","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Payment processing seems like it should be commodity. Use Stripe, accept payments, done."}]]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"But if your business has any complexity beyond simple charges, Stripe becomes a Procrustean bed. Complex billing cycles, multiple payment methods, regulatory requirements, chargeback handling, reconciliation."}]]}],["$","p","2",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"We have built 15+ custom payment systems. Here is when Stripe is enough and when you need custom."}]]}],["$","h2","3",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"What Stripe Does Well"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Stripe is excellent at:"}]]}],["$","li","5",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"One-time charges"}]]}],["$","li","6",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Recurring billing with subscriptions"}]]}],["$","li","7",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Payment method tokenization and storage"}]]}],["$","li","8",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Handling PCI compliance for you"}]]}],["$","li","9",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Multi-currency support"}]]}],["$","li","10",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Fraud detection"}]]}],["$","p","11",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"For most businesses with simple payment needs, Stripe is the right choice."}]]}],["$","h2","12",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"Where Stripe Falls Apart"}],["$","h3","13",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"1. Complex Billing Models"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Stripe charges per subscription. If you have tiered pricing, usage-based billing, or complex discounting, modeling this in Stripe requires workarounds."}]]}],["$","h3","15",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"2. Multiple Payment Methods"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Stripe focuses on cards. If you need to accept bank transfers, check payments, cryptocurrency, or regional payment methods (Alipay, WeChat Pay), Stripe is not the hub."}]]}],["$","h3","17",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"3. Reconciliation"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"When you reconcile your accounting records with your bank statement, they often do not match. Stripe does not model this complexity well."}]]}],["$","h3","19",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"4. Chargeback Handling"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"High-chargeback businesses (D2C, fitness, digital products, travel) need sophisticated chargeback prevention and management. Stripe handles basic cases but not well."}]]}],["$","h3","21",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"5. Regulatory Complexity"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"PCI compliance is one thing. But fintech businesses have other compliance requirements (AML, KYC, transaction reporting, interest calculations). Stripe does not handle these."}]]}],["$","h2","23",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"When Custom Payment Processing Makes Sense"}],["$","p","24",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"You have complex billing."}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Usage-based pricing, tiered pricing, volume discounts, revenue sharing, or complex subscription models."}]]}],["$","p","25",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"You need multiple payment methods."}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Cards are just the start. You need bank transfers, cryptocurrency, digital wallets."}]]}],["$","p","26",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"You have regulatory requirements."}],["$","span","2",{"children":" If you are a fintech company, insurance platform, or business with special compliance needs, custom is necessary."}]]}],["$","p","27",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"High transaction volume with margin."}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Every percentage point of payment processing costs matters. Custom gives you more control."}]]}],["$","p","28",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"International expansion."}],["$","span","2",{"children":" You need to handle multiple currencies, payment methods per region, and local compliance. Custom gives you flexibility."}]]}],["$","h2","29",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"The Architecture"}],["$","h3","30",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Tokenization Layer"}],["$","p","31",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Never store raw payment data. Tokenize it at entry and store only tokens."}]]}],["$","h3","32",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Transaction Engine"}],["$","p","33",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Process transactions through your system, not directly to payment processors. This allows you to apply business logic (limits, rules, validation) before processing."}]]}],["$","h3","34",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Settlement and Reconciliation"}],["$","p","35",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Batch process transactions for settlement. Reconcile daily against bank statements."}]]}],["$","h3","36",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"Fraud and Risk"}],["$","p","37",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Monitor transactions for fraudulent patterns. Decline high-risk transactions."}]]}],["$","h2","38",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"Real Example: High-Growth D2C Brand"}],["$","p","39",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"A direct-to-consumer beauty brand was using Stripe but hitting limitations:"}]]}],["$","li","40",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Subscription model:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Customers on various subscription tiers with gift cards and discounts. Modeling this in Stripe required 3 separat